{"tid":2002181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社報道反送中示威獲普立茲突發新聞攝影獎","createTime":"2020-05-05T05:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T15:02:30.000Z","uid":9030,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56e65212d45d4079e10eff3d011860dc76fa9a5d","tid":2002181,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"美國新聞界最高榮譽普立茲獎（Pulitzer Prize）周一（4日）公布本年度得獎名單。路透社攝影記者以鏡頭記錄去年香港的反修訂《逃犯條例》示威衝突，獲得突發新聞攝影獎。<br />\n<br />\n路透社獲獎的照片記錄香港示威者與警方之間的激烈衝突，包括警方施放催淚彈、橡膠子彈及示威者投擲磚頭。路透社總編Stephen J. Adler表示，攝影記者捕捉到香港示威的規模，照片出色、充滿啟發及令人難忘。獲獎照片可查看普立茲獎網站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200505/s00005/1588652687843/路透社報道港反修例示威-獲普立茲突發新聞攝影獎\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200505%2Fs00005%2F1588652687843%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E7%8D%B2%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%8B%E8%8C%B2%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=e0a0f7c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200505%2Fs00005%2F1588652687843%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E7%8D%B2%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%8B%E8%8C%B2%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E&h=60c7e97a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200505/s00005/1588652687843/路透社報道港反修例示威-獲普立茲突發新聞攝影獎</a>"},{"pid":"4ef6523cd073c52efaa3c2a10adc6fc52b8c6de5","tid":2002181,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QmiGLS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QmiGLS.jpg&h=31d54c37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3139cd3f00ef1b86295331f5945118bfefe601d4","tid":2002181,"uid":9